emerging: We have some idea of the resources we require to operationalise our Impact Management Capability.
expanding: We have a clear plan of the resources required to effectively operationalise our Impact Management Capability.
optimising: There is ongoing work to support the effective operationalisation of the Capability.
mature: We have the optimum resources in place to execute our Impact Management Capability purpose.

nascent: We do not fully understand the resources we require to execute the basic Impact Management function.
